                'preview' => '	[{"id":"preset-root","type":"section","tagName":"div","attributes":{"attrs":{},"style":{"min-height":"150px","width":"600px","padding":"10px 10px 10px 10px","margin":"0 auto"}},"overrideAttributes":{"width":"600px"},"children":[{"type":"Gap","tagName":"div","meta":{"displayName":"Gap","imgSrc":"/images/builder/gap.svg","imgAlt":"gap-widget"},"attributes":{"attrs":{},"style":{"height":"20px"},"containerStyle":{"padding":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}},"overrideAttributes":{},"content":"","id":"MKL2iypYt"},{"type":"Paragraph","tagName":"preview-text-editor","meta":{"displayName":"Paragraph","imgSrc":"/images/builder/paragraph.svg","imgAlt":"paragraph-widget"},"attributes":{"props":{"toolbar":false},"style":{"color":"#000000","font-size":"16px","font-weight":400,"font-style":"normal","text-decoration":"none","align":"left","text-align":"left","outline":"none","font-family":"Helvetica","line-height":"1.6","heading-size":"0px"},"containerStyle":{"padding":"10px 10px 10px 10px"}},"overrideAttributes":{},"content":"<div>Can you imagine that you have the superpower to read everyone\'s mind?</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>You know their desires and challenges without them telling you.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Every word you say, speaks right to their heart.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>They feel like you are the only one who truly understands them.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Ultimately, you can easily sell anything to anyone!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>How cool is that!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>But back to reality, is this possible?</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Yes!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>With the help of technology, you can have similar mind-reading power applicable to your business.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Really? How?</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Hypershapes&rsquo; powerful <strong>Customer Relationship Management System (CRM) will track every of your customers and record their actions!</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><em>Which pages have they visited?</em></div>\n<div><em>&nbsp;</em></div>\n<div><em>What products have they seen?</em></div>\n<div><em>&nbsp;</em></div>\n<div><em>What products are they interested in, but haven&rsquo;t bought yet?</em></div>\n<div><em>&nbsp;</em></div>\n<div><em>What products did they purchase?</em></div>\n<div><em>&nbsp;</em></div>\n<div><em>How much did they spend?</em></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>There is so much more data being recorded!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>It&rsquo;s like giving you all the information about your customers without them telling you!</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>The best part is...</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>You can use this useful information on hand to <strong>upsell them with higher-priced products &amp; services!</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>And you can win their hearts by providing world-class support.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>In short, Hypershapes CRM gives you the superpower to make more profits!</div>","id":"yDHpRO5Qr"},{"type":"Button","tagName":"a","meta":{"displayName":"Button","imgSrc":"/images/builder/button.svg","imgAlt":"button-widget"},"attributes":{"attrs":{"href":"https://help.hypershapes.com/help/crm","target":"_blank"},"style":{"width":"max-content","max-width":"600px","display":"block","color":"#3366BB","background-color":"#FFFFFF","border":"none","border-radius":"2px","cursor":"pointer","padding":"10px 10px 10px 0px","font-size":"16px","font-family":"Helvetica","font-weight":400,"font-style":"normal","text-decoration":"underline","line-height":"1.6","align":"left","margin":"0 auto 0 0","pointer-events":"none"},"containerStyle":{"padding":"10px 10px 10px 10px"}},"overrideAttributes":{},"content":" Click here to find out more!","id":"Q7kR0ak2k"},{"type":"Paragraph","tagName":"preview-text-editor","meta":{"displayName":"Paragraph","imgSrc":"/images/builder/paragraph.svg","imgAlt":"paragraph-widget"},"attributes":{"props":{"toolbar":false},"style":{"color":"#000